OL,5, Billy Connolly has appeared in hundreds
OL,6, of films, documentaries and shows over 
OL,7, the years.                             
OL,9,FBut Big Banana Feet is a rarity. A raw,
OL,10,Fedgy fly-on-the-wall documentary which 
OL,11,Ffollows the comedian, on the cusp of   
OL,12,Ffame, around a volatile landscape.     
OL,14,FThe film was made in 1975 at the height
OL,15,Fof the Troubles in Northern Ireland.   
OL,17,FJust a week before his appearance,     
OL,18,Fthree musicians from a popular cabaret 
OL,19,Fband were shot and killed by a         
OL,20,Fparamilitary group while touring       
OL,21,FIreland.                               
